relatedBlades.copy:
Calling all Partner SE's! We invite you to join us at Industrious Uptown, Charlotte for learning, live demo, and networking amongst your peers! In addition to seeing the latest and greatest from Cloudflare, all attendees will be entered to win __an Ooni Karu 12 Multi-Fuel Pizza Oven!__ Increase your chances to win by completing the following, prior to the event: - Accredited Sales Engineer Training (1 entry) - Zero Trust 101 Training (1 entry) - Area 1 101 Training (1 entry) - Magic Transit 101 Training (1 entry) All training sessions can be accessed via the [Partner Portal](https://portal.cloudflarepartners.com/English/?ReturnUrl=%2fEnglish%2fPartner%2fhome.aspx). Please reach out to Lauren Lidsky (llidsky@cloudflare.com) if you need access to the portal. __Details__
__Date__: Wednesday, 1 March 2023
__Time__: 1:00PM- 3:30PM EST
__Location__: [Virtually](https://cloudflare.zoom.us/webinar/register/WN_To8pL9TISzCCsuvp5xtnMA) or in person at Industrious Uptown, 101 South Tryon Street, Suite 2700, Conference Room B, Charlotte, NC 28280 ([Map](https://breather.com/invite/-4eG_lqWGkU?utm_medium=clipboard&utm_campaign=share-reservation&utm_source=clipboard&utm_term=web))

__How to Register__
*Attending virtually?* [Register here](https://cloudflare.zoom.us/webinar/register/WN_To8pL9TISzCCsuvp5xtnMA)
*Attending in person?* Fill out the form on this page

__Complete the training, attend the event, and be entered to win!__
